<p><strong>Medium humanoid (human, shapechanger), chaotic evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 11 (in humanoid form, 12 in wolf or hybrid form)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 58 (9d8+18)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft. (40 ft. in wolf form)</p>

